title: DLC03
longDescription:
# Features

- New region: The Farmstead!
- Endless Quest: Survive as long as you can while getting lost in time and space, confronted by unending waves of enemies new and old, pushing ever closer to the Comet's epicenter.
- Twisted new trinkets, available for purchase from the Jeweler.
- All-New Enemy Faction: The Miller and his loyal workmen have become eerie husks of their former selves.
- 3 new bosses - The Miller, The Thing From the Stars, and the Comet itself!
- Expand your Hamlet with 4 new District buildings and reap their benefits.
